z string lib
------------

A little lib for making string handling more comfortable

(c) Jaroslaw Szpilewski http://nntp.pl

GPL V2


zstr.c/h
--------
The base zstr data structure. Used by the rest of the library.

zstrlist.c/h
------------
A data structure that holds a list of zstrs.

zstr_split.c/h
--------------
functions to split a C string into a list of zstrs.
